arStrings.szText: “Ugh… I didn’t pay attention to where I collected it from.”
Irritated. Rolls eyes then snatches the item away from the Player. Zurke then tastes a piece of raw human flesh like it's not big deal.
Hmm, yes. This, uh, this corpse was treated with (smacks lips) Serpent Thorn and uh... (smacks lips) Oh yes. Blood Fungus.
Thoughtful/Pondering. Pauses in between ingredient names as he remembers them
